The purpose upon which the School was founded is to provide quality education and training in the selected course for East Texas area residents. The course(s) selected in which to offer instruction all relate to the Barber?Styling Career and the School strives to:

A.	Educate all students in men's and women's haircutting, styling, perming, coloring and proper skin care;

